title: Bug 114470[Smoke] Error message throws when using new Date("3/2/2005") as value in table filter.

OB: When using the code "new Date("3/2/2005")" as a value in the table filter, an error message is displayed.

SR:

2. Enter the value "new Date("3/2/2005")".
